======================================================================
Part 3: Omega_p = |A_p| - rank(constraints)
surplus = excess_paths - rank = (|A_p| - C) - rank
======================================================================

  n=5, p=2:
    avg |A_p| - C = 5.2, avg rank = 6.0, avg surplus = -0.8
    Identity: surplus = excess_paths - rank: True
    avg survival = surplus/excess = -0.2083

